    <h1>JavaScript SEO</h1>
    <p class="description">The practice of ensuring search engines can crawl, render, and index content that JavaScript generates. <strong>65% of JS-dependent pages have indexing issues</strong> versus 8% of server-rendered pages.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
